In order for the first syntax to work, the checkstyle-config.xml should have:

    &lt;module name=&quot;NoWhitespaceBefore&quot;&gt;
      &lt;property name=&quot;id&quot; value=&quot;nowhitespacebefore&quot;/&gt;
    &lt;/module&gt;

