            &lt;/goals&gt;
        &lt;/execution&gt;
    &lt;/executions&gt;
&lt;/plugin&gt;
```

Generate the jacoco report by running the following command in your terminal:
```bash
mvn jacoco:prepare-agent test install jacoco:report
